pageContext.description: Typology: flattened midrib with broad hollowed edge bevels; double notches at butt are neat and deliberate; can't tell whether reworked after breakage, Condition: extant piece in two joining fragments; extremely mutilated making edges jagged and wavy; much denting of faces; bottom-most break is totally crished flat from both faces.
